  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the trial is to evaluate the dose-response relationship with regards
      to change in immunological parameters and safety for SLITone ULTRA house dust mite mix in
      adult subjects with moderate to severe HDM allergic rhinitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
